#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:175
#, no-c-format
msgid "Frequently asked questions"
msgstr "Korduma kippuvad küsimused"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:180
#, no-c-format
msgid "I want to change the way this game looks. Can I?"
msgstr "Ma soovin muuta mängu välimust. On see võimalik?"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:181
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "Currently the only thing you can change about the game look is the color "
#| "of the lines. To do so use <menuchoice><guimenu>Settings</"
#| "guimenu><guimenuitem>Configure &ksquares;...</guimenuitem></menuchoice> "
#| "on the menubar. See <link linkend=\"configuration\">Game Configuration</"
#| "link> section for details."
msgid ""
"Currently the only thing you can change about the game look is the color of "
"the lines. To do so use the <menuchoice><guimenu>Settings</guimenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Configure &ksquares;…</guimenuitem></menuchoice> menu item. See "
"<link linkend=\"configuration\">Game Configuration</link> section for "
"details."
msgstr ""
"Praegu saab muuta ainult joonte värvi. Selleks kasuta menüükäsku "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Seadistused</guimenu><guimenuitem>&ksquares;i "
"seadistamine...</guimenuitem></menuchoice> Täpsemalt kõneleb sellest osa "
"<link linkend=\"configuration\">Mängu seadistamine</link>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:184
#, no-c-format
msgid "I have made a mistake. Can I undo?"
msgstr "Tegin vea. Kas selle saab tagasi võtta?"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:185
#, no-c-format
msgid "No. &ksquares; doesn't currently have an <quote>Undo</quote> feature."
msgstr "Ei, &ksquares; ei paku veel <quote>tagasivõtmise</quote> võimalust."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:188
#, no-c-format
msgid "Can I use the keyboard to play the game?"
msgstr "Kas mängida saab ka klaviatuuri abil?"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:189
#, no-c-format
msgid "No. &ksquares; cannot be played using keyboard."
msgstr "Ei, &ksquares;it ei saa mängida klaviatuuri abil."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:192
#, no-c-format
msgid "I cannot figure out what to do here! Are there hints?"
msgstr "Ma ei saa aru, mida ma peaksin tegema! Kas mingeid vihjeid ei ole?"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:193
#, no-c-format
msgid "No. There is no <quote>Hint</quote> feature implemented yet."
msgstr "Ei, <quote>salvestamise</quote> võimalus veel puudub."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:196
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"I have to quit the game now, but I am not finished yet. Can I save my "
"progress?"
msgstr ""
"Ma pean mängust väljuma, aga mäng ei ole veel läbi. Kas ma saan oma seisu "
"salvestada?"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:197
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "No. &ksquares; doesn't currently have an <quote>Undo</quote> feature."
msgid "&ksquares; does not have a <quote>Save</quote> feature."
msgstr "Ei, &ksquares; ei paku veel <quote>tagasivõtmise</quote> võimalust."

#. Tag: title
