msgid "New Game Dialog"
msgstr "Uue mängu dialoog"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:213
#, no-c-format
msgid "New game"
msgstr "Uus mäng"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:217
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The <guilabel>New Game</guilabel> dialog consistes of the following "
"groupboxes:"
msgstr "Dialoog <guilabel>Uus mäng</guilabel> koosneb järgmistest osadest:"

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:220
#, no-c-format
msgid "Players"
msgstr "Mängijad"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:221
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "Here you can change the number of participating players, as well as "
#| "determine who will be played by human and who by the artificial "
#| "intelligence. Use the <guilabel>Number of players</guilabel> selection "
#| "box to specify the number of participants. Then type a name for each "
#| "participant and use the check box to specify the player type."
msgid ""
"Here you can change the number of participating players, as well as "
"determine who will be played by human and who by the artificial "
"intelligence. Use the <guilabel>Number of players:</guilabel> spin-box to "
"specify the number of participants. Then type a name for each participant "
"and use the <guilabel>Human?</guilabel> check box to specify the player type."
msgstr ""
"Siin saab muuta mängijate arvu ning ka määrata, milliseid neist mängivad "
"inimesed ja milliseid tehisaju. Valikukastiga <guilabel>Mängijate arv</"
"guilabel> saab paika panna mängijate arvu. Seejärel kirjuta kõigi mängijate "
"nimed ja kasuta märkekasti nende tüübi määramiseks."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:224
#, no-c-format
msgid "Game Board"
msgstr "Mängulaud"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:225
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "Here you can regulate the size of the game board. Use the "
#| "<guilabel>Width</guilabel> and <guilabel>Height</guilabel> selection "
#| "boxes to change the width and height of the game board."
msgid ""
"Here you can regulate the size of the game board. Use the <guilabel>Width:</"
"guilabel> and <guilabel>Height:</guilabel> spin-boxes to change the width "
"and height of the game board."
msgstr ""
"Siin saab paika panna mängulaua suuruse. Valikukastidega <guilabel>Laius</"
"guilabel> ja <guilabel>Kõrgus</guilabel> saab määrata vastavalt mängulaua "
"laiuse ja kõrguse."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:228
#, no-c-format
msgid "Game Settings"
msgstr "Mängu seadistused"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:229
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This part of the configuration dialog regulates the difficulty of the game. "
"If you leave the <guilabel>Quick start</guilabel> check box unchecked - the "
"game will begin with the empty grid. Otherwise the game will start with the "
"game board partially filled."
msgstr ""
"Siin saab muuta mängu raskusastet. Kui jätta märkimata kastike "
"<guilabel>Kiirkäivitus</guilabel>. alustatakse mängi tühja võrgustikuga, "
"vastasel juhul on mängulaud juba eelnevalt osaliselt täidetud."

